    <div class="vd-wrap">

      <p>I will admit something. When I started this piece, I expected a story about a marketing gimmick. I have written about enough hair-care launches to know what those look like. The first time I clipped a Velvy "D" into my own hair, I was prepared to be unimpressed. <strong>The second time I leaned back against my car seat, I noticed the absence.</strong> The small, dull pressure I had been carrying without knowing it was gone.</p>

