        <h2>Quick answers</h2>
        <details>
          <summary>Will the magnets hold a thick chignon?</summary>
          <p>Yes. Velvy "D" uses neodymium N52 magnets, the same grade as industrial fasteners. It holds a thick mid-length to long chignon without slipping, even during workouts.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Is it safe near my phone, cards or pacemaker?</summary>
          <p>The magnetic field is fully contained between the two plates when closed. It does not affect phones or contactless cards in normal use. If you have a pacemaker, follow your physician's general guidance on magnetic accessories.</p>
